race.description: Greyhounds As Pets (N/P) Tg 5+W Series 2 F Pr2
race.comment: GOLDEN GANGSTER (8) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (20.12) behind Mr. Zing Zang at this track. Has performed well from this box with a win and eight minor placings to his name from 17 starts. Winning claims. SLIPPER'S SOLO (7) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.94 beating STARBURST CANDY. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Capable of going well again. SMOOTH VIXEN (1) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Continues to race well, filling the minors at the last three starts, the latest when third (20.21) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Deserves a win and gets her chance. DARK QUEEN (2) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.
